## Game Mode [/gameModes/{gameMode}]
    
### /gameModes/{gameMode} [GET]

Fetches info for a game mode

+ Parameter
    + gameMode - String game mode all lower case, using dashes instead of space
    
+ Response 200 (applicaton/json)
    
        "example": [
            "The Dark Star Rises": {
                "Playable Champions": [
                    "Thresh"
                ],
                "Items": [
                    "None"
                ],
                "SummonerSpells": [
                    "None"
                ],
                "Lore": "Thresh spooky"
            }, 
            "Summoners Rift": {
                "Playable Champions": [
                    "Lux",
                    "Aatrox",
                    "Caitlyn",
                    "etc."
                ],
                "Items": [
                    "Duskblade",
                    "BoTRK",
                    "etc."
                ],
                "Lore": "will populate with real lore" 
            }
        ]
 
 
 
 
        
