## Match Details [/matches/matchHistory/{matchID}]

### /matches/matchHistory/{matchID} [GET]

Fetches details about a specific match.

+ Parameter
    + matchID - ID of the match you are looking up

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
        "example": [
            "matchDetails": {
                "MatchID: 4819434182,
                "Participants": {
                    "Participant1": {
                        "champion": "Annie",
                        "summonerID": 4819434182,
                        "Items": [
                            {
                                "ID": "Doran's Ring",
                                "count": 1
                            },
                            {
                                "ID": "Manamune",
                                "count": 1
                            },
                            {
                                "ID": "Zhonya's Hourglass",
                                "count": 1
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "Participant2": {
                        "etc....." : "adsfasd"
                    },
                    ...
                },
                "Map": "Summoner's Rift",
                "Game Mode": "ARAM",
                "TimeLength": 30:21,
                "Winning Team": "Blue",
                "MatchDetails: [
                    ...
